headline: Wrong-way Biden dispatches Kamala Harris ... to the Ukraine border
author: Monica Showalter
sentences: According to the New York Post: Vice President Kamala Harris set off Thursday on a peace mission to Europe as Russia appeared to accelerate preparations for an invasion of Ukraine — undeterred by her failure to resolve the ongoing US-Mexico border crisis as President Biden’s point person on illegal immigration.
